<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880712-0082 </DOCNO><HL> Dividend News: Southland Communications Inc. </HL><SO> </SO><CO> SCII </CO><IN> DIV </IN><TEXT>   SOUTHLAND COMMUNICATIONS Inc. declared a 2-for-1 stock split on its common stock. The Santa Ana, Calif.-based paging concern said it expects the payable date for the split to be Aug. 23 to stock of record on the same date. The company currently has 897,728 shares outstanding. </TEXT></DOC>